 line- Sullivan Square and Community College stations.  -Walking distance to Whole Foods, CVS -Short drive to Target, Stop & Shop, Starbucks Your room contains: -Full sized bed -Flat screen  -Roku media player for Netflix and Pandora, etc. (Sorry, no cable) -Free Wifi -Fresh Linens/Towels',7,1,'MA','US',150,'',0,1,1125,'Apartment','Entire home/apt',5,'2','2','3'),(548184,5182313,'https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/5182313','Sunny musicians apt. close to T!','Welcome to our home! We (Rachel and Adam) live in a lovely 2bd apartment in Boston\'s Jamaica Plain neighborhood. We are friendly folks who love hosting travelers in our JP apartment in our 2nd bedroom. Our adorable dog Lucy loves meeting new people and will melt your heart! We love making breakfast for our guests and sharing our favorite spots to visit and eat at in the city. Just a 5 min walk to the T, we love our location and welcome you to our home! The space is ideal for solo travelers or couples. The bedroom has a full size bed with really cozy sheets, window a/c for the hotter summer months, and heat for the winter! The room has a nice bookshelf, comfy armchair, and small closet. Our super friendly beagle/collie Lucy will melt your heart. She is very affectionate family friendly dog who loves to meet new guests. We also very much enjoy cooking for our guests, and we are happy to provide breakfast for you during your stay. Just let us know if you would like a hot breakfast of eggs',12,1,'MA','US',110,'5',10,2,7,'Apartment','Entire home/apt',2,'1','0','1'),(26853841,5191658,'https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/5191658','Beautiful New 8 Downtown Boston','Open loft in the middle of the city. 5 minute walk to the Financial District, South Station and T stop, and the train to NYC. Located in a newly renovated historic building with all the original brick and beams. Above the French Bastille Kitchen. This airy loft has an open layout with brick walls and hard wood floors throughout.  The main room has four large windows that